OL,3,CDeaf boy, 10, wants to help others
OL,4,Cafter therapy helped him communicate
OL,6,FA deaf 10-year-old boy is calling for
OL,7,Fauditory-verbal therapy to be more
OL,8,Fwidely available for deaf children in
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FAuditory-verbal therapy is a method
OL,12,Ffor teaching deaf children to listen
OL,13,Fand speak using hearing technology.
OL,15,FNathaniel Darian, 10, from Penarth,
OL,16,Falong with Harrison Steeple, 26,
OL,17,Fvisited the Senedd on Tuesday, 16
OL,18,FJuly, to call on MSs to invest in the
OL,19,Ffuture of deaf children after both
OL,20,Fwere supported with their hearing
OL,21,Fthrough this therapy.
