OL,3,CDeaf boy, 10, wants to help others
OL,4,Cafter therapy helped him communicate
OL,6,FShe said: "Deafness is a disability
OL,7,Fbut with the right support deaf babies
OL,8,Fand children like Nathaniel can
OL,9,Fachieve their potential."
OL,11,FShe added: "Thanks to the amazing
OL,12,Fcochlear implant technology and the
OL,13,Fspecialist auditory verbal therapy
OL,14,Fprogramme he is reaching his academic
OL,15,Ftargets as he should. The charity
OL,16,FAuditory Verbal UK (AVUK) played an
OL,17,Fimportant part in helping make our
OL,18,Fdreams for Nathaniel's speech and
OL,19,Flistening come true.
