OL,4,Cafter therapy helped him communicate
OL,6,FAVUK's Hear Us Now campaign is calling
OL,7,Ffor urgent investment to enable all
OL,8,Fdeaf children, whose families want
OL,9,Fthem to learn to listen and talk, to
OL,10,Faccess auditory verbal therapy through
OL,11,Fexisting public services close to
OL,12,Fwhere they live.
OL,14,FAccording to the charity's figures,
OL,15,Fmore than 80% of deaf children (rising
OL,16,Fto 97% of children without additional
OL,17,Fneeds) who attend an auditory verbal
OL,18,Ftherapy programme for at least two
OL,19,Fyears achieve spoken language skill on
OL,20,Fa par with their hearing peers.
