OL,6,FDespite this, 90% of deaf children who
OL,7,Fcould benefit from auditory verbal
OL,8,Ftherapy are unable to access it.
OL,10,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"Auditory verbal therapy targets
OL,12,Fdeveloping spoken language through
OL,13,Flistening, it is not suitable for
OL,14,Fevery deaf child. Health professionals
OL,15,Fwill select the appropriate treatment
OL,16,Fmode for the individual.
